<p class=3D"MsoPlainText" style=3D"text-indent:.5in">So it&#8217;s up to yo=
u to insist upon and shape an informed debate.&nbsp; Imagine if Benjamin Fr=
anklin had seen that senator with the snowball, what he would think.&nbsp; =
Imagine if your 5th grade science teacher had seen that.&nbsp;
 (Laughter.)&nbsp; He&#8217;d get a D.&nbsp; (Laughter.)&nbsp; And he&#8217=
