<p class=3D"MsoPlainText" style=3D"text-indent:.5in">Look, I'm not suggesti=
ng that cold analysis and hard data are ultimately more important in life t=
han passion, or faith, or love, or loyalty.&nbsp; I am suggesting that thos=
e highest expressions of our humanity can
 only flourish when our economy functions well, and proposed budgets add up=
, and our environment is protected.&nbsp; And to accomplish those things, t=
