ecause of you!&nbsp; (Applause.)&nbsp;
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-indent:.5in"><span style=3D"font-size:=
11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span>=
</p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-indent:.5in"><span style=3D"font-size:=
11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif">THE PRESIDENT:&nbsp; Wel=
l, that's nice.&nbsp; I mean, I helped, but -- (applause.)<o:p></o:p></span=
></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-indent:.5in"><span style=3D"font-size:=
11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span>=
</p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-indent:.5in"><span style=3D"font-size:=
11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif">Look, if you want to cha=
nge this country for the better, you better start participating.&nbsp; I'll=
 give you an example on a lot of people&#8217;s minds right
 now -- and that&#8217;s the growing inequality in our economy.&nbsp; Over =
much of the last century, we&#8217;ve unleashed the strongest economic engi=
ne the world has ever seen, but over the past few decades, our economy has =
