 of earners now take in half of all income in the U.S.&nbsp; In the past, i=
t used to be a top CEO made 20 or 30 times the income of the average worker=
.&nbsp; Today, it&#8217;s 300 times more.&nbsp; And wages aren&#8217;t risi=
ng fast enough for millions of hardworking families.&nbsp;
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Ca=
libri&quot;,sans-serif"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-indent:.5in"><span style=3D"font-size:=
11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif">Now, if we want to rever=
