 that represents your views, you will get what you want.&nbsp; And if you o=
pt out, or stop paying attention, you won&#8217;t.&nbsp; It&#8217;s that si=
mple. (Applause.)&nbsp; It's not that complicated.
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Ca=
libri&quot;,sans-serif"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-indent:.5in"><span style=3D"font-size:=
11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif">Now, one of the reasons =
