ither way, you win.&nbsp; And more importantly, our democracy wins.&nbsp; (=
Applause.)&nbsp;
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Ca=
